data.description: Come home to a well-built luxury home in the Cloisters of Fayette County. This home has 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, double sized fireplace in the living area, granite counter tops in the kitchen, a dining area, and sitting area, in the kitchen, along with a great open concept. The Master Bedroom is 20x26 with a sitting area for relaxation, and doors that leads to the covered Lanai. The master bathroom suite is 18x14 and have 3 separate shower heads for taking a shower. Come see this home.
